law.history: Repealed 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 31. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 84, sec. 46. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1020-6.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Court to make rules governing assignment of civil actions -- Criminal prosecutions -- Proceedings on bail bonds and recognizances.
